title: Henderson: Sorting out the prep football playoffs
text:
Henderson: Sorting out the prep football playoffs Kyle Henderson Talk about it in NEW MEXICO PREP FOOTBALL INSIDER 
The Sandia victory over Eldorado Friday Night caused a massive amount of playoff picture shake up. Today, Kyle Henderson of NMPreps.com breaks down each district and reveals his latest playoff predictions for October 17th, 2015.
